name: lyla bright
description:
Her presence is calming, and she inspires people to be honest and pure.

collection name (Inside And Outside woman )

These lines come from the time that I was full of imagination.
I used these lines to arrive at the concept of women’s inner complexity.
Women are beautiful and calm from the outside
But from the inside they are full of spiritual conflicts for their evolution
Being a woman is one of the most difficult challenges in the world
